Package ghidra.docking.settings

Class FloatingPointPrecisionSettingsDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • ghidra.docking.settings.FloatingPointPrecisionSettingsDefinition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EnumSettingsDefinition, SettingsDefinition
    public class FloatingPointPrecisionSettingsDefinition
extends java.lang.Object
implements EnumSettingsDefinition
    SettingsDefinition to define the number of digits of precision to show. The value is rendered to thousandths, 3 digits of precision, by default.
